raw_desc: 6-in-1 Power Strip: the ugreen extension cord equipped with 1 USB-C port, 3 USB-A ports, and 2 AC outlets. Living room, office, kitchen and other places, this is enough! 2990W Fast Charging: USB C power strip supports PD3.0, QC3.0, FCP, AFC and other protocols. The AC outlet has a maximum power of 2990W (MAX 13A/250V) and the USB C port features 20W fast charging, making it easy to quickly charge mobile phones, laptops, tablets and cameras. You can charge iPhone 16 from 0 to 54% in just 30 minutes (Note: The output power of the USB multiport may vary, please refer to the picture below for more information) Intelligent Protection: The UGREEN power strip passed CE+UKCA+SafetyMark certification, safe to use. It is equipped with a GaN chip and also has over-current, over-voltage, overload, and short-circuit protection functions, it can protect your safety at any time. Not only that, the smart power strip can also reliably turn on and off automatically to protect your valuable electronic equipment (Note: To achieve overload protection, the switch button feels loose) Clean and Organized: UGREEN USB fast charging plug features a side USB port design , which can save space and keep your desktop tidy. It allows you to easily use multiple equipment anywhere where sockets are limited. Wide Compatibility: The power strip is compatible with almost all equipment from the latest mobile phones to smart home appliances. Such as Galaxy S25, iPhone 16/17, Google Pixel 9, iPad Pro, AirPods Pro and more Suitable for Multiple Scenarios: One is enough! The ultra-light and compact design of the wall power strip and measures only 10.5*7.5*3.5cm, makes it ideal for various scenarios. What You Get: 1* power strip, 1*user manual, 24-month warranty, 24-hour customer service, lifetime technical support.
